List Received Secrtes <p>To find a list of secrets you've been sent use the <code>secret list</code> command;</p> <pre><code>pigeonhole secret list
</code></pre> <p>Once you know the secret reference of the secret you want to retrieve;</p> <pre><code>    pigeonhole secret collect --reference &lt;reference&gt;
</code></pre> <p>You can also use the <code>--filepath</code> to override the path used to decrypt and extract your secret</p>
